sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagrama de secuencia FSD-UC-004 - Generar orden de compra y QR de pago
  autonumber
  participant U as Asistente
  participant WEB as Landing/Checkout
  participant API as Core API
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant PAY as Adaptador QR
  participant BANK as Proveedor QR

  U->>WEB: Selecciona ticket y cantidad
  WEB->>API: POST /orders (eventId, ticketTypeId, buyer)
  API->>DB: Validar cupo y reservar temporalmente
  DB-->>API: Cupo reservado (TTL = expires_at)
  API->>DB: Crear orden status=pending
  API->>PAY: createPaymentQr(orderId, amount)
  PAY->>BANK: Solicitar QR de cobro
  BANK-->>PAY: paymentReference + payload QR
  PAY-->>API: Referencia + QR
  API->>DB: Persistir payments(status=pending, reference)
  API-->>WEB: { orderId, paymentReference, paymentQr }
  WEB-->>U: Mostrar QR escaneable y countdown
